reviews.review_text: Okay You Want a review! Two words for you - Ollin Agrageed! Don't know what it means, don't care. This shit is the fly! This recording crackles and hums like a vault release. This version here is full of Jerry licks, hand clapping, strange sitar likes soundings, Phil is dancing like a hippie chick all over this stuff... These shows should be a box set, why they dragged out a tired Egypt run I'll never know.
10-22-78 I'm pretty sure Ollin Arrageed is a song that they play for the bride and groom at Egyptian weddings. Anyhow this is a wonderfull show and recording.

better than road trips the climax of an amazing winterland run.
after listening to "olin arrageed" and comparing to road trips, one can see how much they butchered it for official release.  Jerry's problably looking down and frowning at those commercial road trips. even with the great intro, the band still manages to reach more peaks during the jamming on mojo fadeaway
